Package com.amplifyframework.analytics

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AnalyticsCategoryBehavior
    Defines the client behavior (client API) consumed by the app for collection and sending of Analytics events.
    AnalyticsEventBehavior
    Defines the interface for analytics events.
    AnalyticsPropertyBehavior<T>
    Encapsulates a value of type T.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalyticsBooleanProperty
    AnalyticsBooleanProperty wraps a Boolean value to store in AnalyticsProperties.
    AnalyticsCategory
    Defines the Client API consumed by the application.
    AnalyticsCategoryConfiguration
    Configuration for Analytics category that also contains configuration for individual plugins.
    AnalyticsDoubleProperty
    AnalyticsDoubleProperty wraps a Double value to store in AnalyticsProperties.
    AnalyticsEvent
    AnalyticsEvent is a custom analytics event that holds a name and a number of AnalyticsProperties.
    AnalyticsEvent.Builder
    Builder is used to create and configure an instance of AnalyticsEvent.
    AnalyticsIntegerProperty
    AnalyticsIntegerProperty wraps an Integer value to store in AnalyticsProperties.
    AnalyticsPlugin<E>
    Abstract class that a plugin implementation of Analytics category would extend.
    AnalyticsProperties
    AnalyticsProperties provides key/value pairs to represent attributes of an AnalyticsEventBehavior.
    AnalyticsProperties.Builder
    Builder is used to create and configure an instance of AnalyticsProperties.
    AnalyticsStringProperty
    AnalyticsStringProperty wraps a String value to store in AnalyticsProperties.
    UserProfile
    Represents user specific data such as name, email, plan, location etc.
    UserProfile.Builder
    Builder for creating a UserProfile object.
    UserProfile.Location
    Represents a user's location.
    UserProfile.Location.Builder
    Builder for creating a Location object.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AnalyticsChannelEventName
    An enumeration of the names of events relating the AnalyticsCategory, that are published via HubCategory.publish(HubChannel, HubEvent) on the HubChannel.DATASTORE channel.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AnalyticsException
    Exception thrown by Analytics category plugins.
